Fite-Nite Of Legends: Global Offensive XV
FNOLGO XV
Shaylan Dias, Ben Gu, Jason Zhu
5/9/18

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Description:
In a world, where nothing seems to make sense anymore, a dark, dangerous, deadly, death match is taking place.
The leaders of the splintered factions have placed heavy bets on their champions to succeed. They hold an annual 
contest to determine the strongest faction of them all to lead their people and rule over all the land. Targeted towards 
battle-royale fanatics of all ages, whose faction are YOU a part of? In this revolutionary, top down, fifteenth edition 
game, YOU will take control of a championand fight to rule over this mysterious new world.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Instructions:
The Objective of the game is to be the last remaining Avatar on the map. You are in an arena with up to 16 other players, each 
with 4 lives. Use your abilities to take down your opponents and be the last one standing in this contest of champions!

Controls:
W-A-S-D - Movement
Space - Dash in direction of movement
Mouse - Aim
Q- Block/Shield
Left Mouse Button - Basic Attack
Right Mouse Button - Ranged Attack
E - Ability 1
R - Ability 2
F - Ability 3

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Feature List:
Must Haves
	Server Networking - DONE
	Menu
	Select server - DONE
